snippet.title: Mei Leaf
snippet.description:
Don and friends invite you to learn and love the most incredible leaf. TEA!

This channel is dedicated to spreading our passion and knowledge about tea and encourage everyone to become a tea connoisseur and lover. No tea bags, just the magic of the real leaf. We cover all types of tea from White tea, Green tea (and Matcha), Oolong tea, Black tea and Puerh (and other prost-fermented) tea.

To visit our teahouse come and find us at https:/meileaf.com

To read Don's blog about tea visit https://meileaf.com/tea-articles/

We offer regular tea lectures and tastings for beginners and enthusiasts to ignite their passion for tea by learning about its history, cultivation and variety of flavours. To book your place just ask or give us a call on 08700 100 023
